      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this peerless specimen, maintained in impeccable showroom condition. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation, exhibiting no discernible wear and adhering to the most rigorous standards of mechanical and aesthetic excellence. A definitive acquisition for the discerning professional seeking uncompromised quality and prestige.",
