      "description": "Presenting an exceptional vehicle in showroom-grade condition. This unit has been meticulously maintained to an impeccable standard, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new. With its flawless aesthetic and peerless mechanical integrity, this represents a premier acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
